text: William Woodgate (26 August 1638 - 18 January 1717) was High Sheriff of Kent in 1700, he was the son of John Woodgate. == Marriage == He married Mary Sillcock of Benenden, Kent in 1658, they had 1 child, William Woodgate (1661-1758) ==References== Category:1638 births Category:1710s deaths Category:People from Kent
title: William Woodgate
